description:
&lt;p&gt;Are you an experienced Support Worker looking for a new position?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Apollo Home Healthcare is seeking experienced Support Workers to care for a young boy with complex care needs.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for dedicated and compassionate Support Workers who are passionate about their job, enjoy delivering one to one support and build positive relationships with our service users and their families.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our young service user is a very special boy who has some highly complex care needs.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;He is a cheeky boy with a brilliant sense of humour, who enjoys watching TV and playing on his iPad.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our ideal applicant will have a fun, outgoing personality and have a genuine interest of working with children.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;To enable you to support his complex needs we provide extensive bespoke training for all his clinical needs.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Essential Experience Required&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;6 months previous care / support work experience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Medication Administration&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Personal Care&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Moving and Handling&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We have the following shifts available:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Day shifts from 7:30 am - 8:00 pm&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Nights shifts from 7:45 pm - 8:00 am&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a personally rewarding role where you can build on your experience, whilst delivering exceptional care and support to our service user and really making an impact on his day to day life.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Why work for Apollo Home Healthcare?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We specialise in the provision of highly complex clinical care services delivered in the homes of service users.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are passionate about delivering the highest standard of care and we recognise that our Nurses, Healthcare Assistants and Support Workers are integral to doing this. In return for your hard work and dedication you will receive:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Flexible hours to suit&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Confirmed rotas&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent rates of pay&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Holiday pay&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Full clinical training&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Opportunity to work with other service users in the area&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ongoing professional training and development&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We need key workers on the front line supporting our service users in the fight against the COVID-19 Pandemic.&lt;/p&gt;
